Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:08.22,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,This is me — Ferrylady at Wangsheng Funeral Parlor. No-one of importance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:13.95,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,This gentleman beside me is our most knowledgeable consultant, Mr. Zhongli
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:21.22,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,This Noctilucous Jade is small, but a beautiful shade of translucent blue. It would be a shame not to buy it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:21.84,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:35.82,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Pasting a Windwheel Aster to wet glaze before it is fired in the kiln? Fascinating. The flower turns to ash, but its shape is forever retained. Such genius — it would be a pity to not purchase this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:36.98,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:44.75,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Cor Lapis is itself hard to gather. It must have taken true skill indeed to unearth two pieces so alike. We should buy them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:45.68,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:50.85,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,A fine Noctilucous Jade... artisan porcelain... and a pair of Cor Lapis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.30,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"And a Windwheel Aster as a gift for the Ferrylady"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:57.10,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Yes, he even got me a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:00.08,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Mr. Zhongli truly is an amazing person
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:08.38,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,When Xiangling is cooking, it would be far more appealing to go to Wanmin Restaurant, as opposed to Xinyue Kiosk or Liuli Pavilion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:13.86,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with anything so long as it's good... But do they only have chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:19.42,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,You will need to be adept with chopsticks if you are to truly appreciate Liyue's gastronomy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:26.48,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Mr. Zhongli, we have Springvale Boar on the menu today — would you like to try it instead of the salt and pepper tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:27.90,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,We'll have both
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:34.00,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"In accordance with Snezhnayan customs, we gave Xiangling a tip for her amazing new dish"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:40.53,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,...Mr. Zhongli values friendly ties over Mora, and is generous in word and deed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:44.74,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Well, the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor often foots the cost of his generosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:51.62,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,But thankfully, the Northland Bank is bearing this particular bill
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:57.58,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Welcome, come in! Excluding this pair of hairpins, everything else is for sale
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.86,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,They're not for sale? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:08.50,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,These are heirlooms pawned by a poor fellow to scrounge together money for his wife's medication
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.79,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,I must hang on to them for him until the redemption period expires
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.18,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:17.52,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"I paid off the shopkeeper, and took this pair of hairpins"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.58,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"Seeking to return them to their owner, with some living expenses on the side"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:31.07,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,"Please help me conceal these expenses in our accounts, would you? I will be sure to buy you lunch"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.37,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Ha, honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:39.01,Genshin Impact,,0,0,0,,Once you become entangled with Mr. Zhongli, there's no getting away from him at all
